tid":2455501,"uid":6788,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T11:25:16.000Z","msg":"小學開始有online game<br />\n同老豆玩金庸 share玩一隻人<br />\n因為自己唔會有錢比月費<br />\n但對升乜野有分歧 最尾佢開咗第2個ac 玩<br />\n但好快冇玩<br />\n直至讀asso見我玩返免費版佢又一齊玩<br />\n然後又跟我玩神抄之塔<br />\n但淨係識轉一兩隻色<br />\n<br />\n近幾年搬埋出去住 佢對眼又開始老花<br />\n已經陪唔到我打機了<br />\n<br />\n好在佢鍾意左行山 到我可以陪佢行"},{"pid":"5a038b1e38cb074d38a693db2417848ee4087936","tid":2455501,"uid":207050,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T11:36:41.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n神魔之塔<br />\n以前中學有玩 玩玩下佢又跟住玩 佢玩到而家 玩咗成7年<br />\n<br />\n有日我堂大佬問佢點仲玩神魔之塔 佢話回憶以前同我玩嘅時光 跟手我望一望老豆塊臉 同我記憶中唔同咗 老咗 皺紋多咗 身體差咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 老竇老母離咗婚 跟咗老母住 一個月先見一兩次老竇"},{"pid":"658e7e6d568515dad2a7ecf4484d25e93cf3617b","tid":2455501,"uid":144773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T11:52:52.000Z","msg":"dad of light<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bbc3cee74d587bf145fcbcab9f11fadf6f6e2e0","tid":2455501,"uid":81559,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T16:53:06.000Z","msg":"啲留言睇到好sad"},{"pid":"bacb8e703b43475f480a480fe810066de8fc7bd0","tid":2455501,"uid":6283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T23:38:47.000Z","msg":"老豆廿幾年前同我打吞食天地2之赤壁  我果陣得3、4歲<br />\n佢鐘意用趙雲 細個唔識控制 成日用張飛捉佢黎咬 之後好似好認真鬧我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n到PS234年代 佢由三國無雙 戰國無雙 開始第一集玩足咁多集 仲話我成績好買遊戲機俾我 其實係佢自己想玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"517794128e5cd05701639949915ae07f7ab827f9","tid":2455501,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bacb8e703b43475f480a480fe810066de8fc7bd0","tid":2455501,"uid":6283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T23:38:47.000Z","msg":"老豆廿幾年前同我打吞食天地2之赤壁  我果陣得3、4歲<br />\n佢鐘意用趙雲 細個唔識控制 成日用張飛捉佢黎咬 之後好似好認真鬧我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n到PS234年代 佢由三國無雙 戰國無雙 開始第一集玩足咁多集 仲話我成績好買遊戲機俾我 其實係佢自己想玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T00:07:12.000Z","msg":"好老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6006b74b12ef9b17e94cfdb37b9312d28d8557c9","tid":2455501,"uid":218941,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T00:30:23.000Z","msg":"冇 老豆好唔中意我打機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中學個陣偷偷地打lol比佢發現 成部電腦比佢拆咗出嚟<br />\n或者搞到我連唔到wifi <br />\n記得有年暑假 每日剩係企係屋企騎樓睇下風景畫下畫<br />\n將屋企啲書睇完一次又一次 等時間可以快啲過<br />\n<br />\n好羨慕其他人嘅爸爸媽媽🥲"},{"pid":"92dc7380fa0991bcc3de1d657666b008a5f02976","tid":2455501,"uid":170187,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a6b67afa2a2775f327ee74ab6ea1f7a05906d2de","tid":2455501,"uid":84102,"like":56,"dislike":0,"score":56,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T07:57:31.000Z","msg":"係咪以前有個新聞定貼文講外國有個仔玩返隻賽車game 有佢過咗身嘅老豆嘅最佳記錄喺度，（即係會見到部虛擬車）佢永遠玩呢隻game都唔會超車過佢老豆嘅記錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為唔想洗走咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T00:32:37.000Z","msg":"Son Finds His Late Dad's 'Ghost' In A Racing Video Game<br />\nFound this story online by 00WARTHERAPY00 and thought it was related and pretty moving!<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Well, when i was 4, my dad bought a trusty XBox. you know, the first, ruggedy, blocky one from 2001. we had tons and tons and tons of fun playing all kinds of games together - until he died, when i was just 6.<br />\n<br />\ni couldnt touch that console for 10 years.<br />\n<br />\nbut once i did, i noticed something.<br />\n<br />\nwe used to play a racing game, Rally Sports Challenge. actually pretty awesome for the time it came.<br />\n<br />\nand once i started meddling around... i found a GHOST.<br />\n<br />\nliteraly.<br />\n<br />\nyou know, when a time race happens, that the fastest lap so far gets recorded as a ghost driver? yep, you guessed it - his ghost still rolls around the track today.<br />\n<br />\nand so i played and played, and played, untill i was almost able to beat the ghost. until one day i got ahead of it, i surpassed it, and...<br />\n<br />\ni stopped right in front of the finish line, just to ensure i wouldnt delete it.<br />\n<br />\nBliss.&quot;"},{"pid":"cffaac1b0b9e9433cef3d91fdd2adcef732ea06e","tid":2455501,"uid":75425,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T00:38:51.000Z","msg":"好細個就同爸爸玩紅白機 佢好有心機教我玩個隻坦克game<br />\n之後大個咗 我用第一份part time搵到嘅錢買ps2 之後就教返佢打機 玩biohazard 4 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢之後打到仲勁過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過宜家佢老了 唔太鍾意打機 得閒就撚下狗 去散下步就一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7070512510e0199b997cb950159f2803cb2c26b2","tid":2455501,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T00:42:30.000Z","msg":"睇老豆玩大波蘿2<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e74ac09753c4376d18aa46b6892237a8b0ed7d83","tid":2455501,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92dc7380fa0991bcc3de1d657666b008a5f02976","tid":2455501,"uid":170187,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a6b67afa2a2775f327